#: ui/app/workrave.metainfo.xml:9
msgid ""
"Workrave is a free program that assists in the recovery and prevention of "
"Repetitive Strain Injury (RSI). It frequently alerts you to take "
"microbreaks, rest breaks and restricts you to your daily computer usage."
msgstr ""
"Workrave 是一款免费软件，用于预防和缓解重复性劳损（RSI）。程序会定时提醒你进"
"行微型休息、长时间休息，并限制每日电脑使用时长。"

